{"tid":852411,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[火星人]岩岩先發現原來iPhone 4S - iOS 6.1.3 有官方認證可以downgrade!","createTime":"2018-10-07T23:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T01:17:47.000Z","uid":16562,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1415a5ea71ae7cc74aed2eaa32fd0c892ad51daa","tid":852411,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"是甘的，小弟本身都知iPhone 4S 係可以由iOS 9.3.5 down grade番去iOS 6<br />\n<br />\n不過就好多野要搞去fake iTunes之類既操作。<br />\n<br />\n但岩岩無聊上網睇到iOS 6原來有番iTunes 官方認證比你downgrade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後拎番部升左iOS 9.3.5 既iPhone 4S出黎 見佢連掃MON都lag到hihi就把心一橫試下得唔得<br />\n<br />\n點知真係比我好簡單咁降番去iOS 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落番iOS 6, 部4S真係即時番生, 開APPS同而家新iPhone既速度有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你又想降既就試下跟以下條link做啦:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZNkS-eOpZWA&amp;t=204s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZNkS-eOpZWA%26t%3D204s&d=VZw3MJ3HFo%2B70rSU20z6msmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=18c08c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZNkS-eOpZWA&amp;t=204s</a><br />\n<br />\n另外因為而家iCloud有雙重認證(2FA), 登入App store &amp; iCloud時有少少麻煩<br />\n要首先 打左密碼, 之後你另一部MAC/iOS機會彈個6位密碼比你<br />\n之後你要再係你部舊機既密碼果欄到打「<strong>ID密碼+6位密碼</strong>」<br />\n<br />\n我知火星左, 但真係教主最後既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年讀中學既回憶番番返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6994d04a1c18523f